1/17/00
  Recode idea:
    After an I picture (or simply a GOP header), the drift needs to be reset
    to 0.  It will remain zero till the first recoded frame.  From that point
    on, we need to update the drift even if there is no recode.

    A flag driftFlag is added to ChanInfo for this purpose.


