  MEMO: brief operation of splicer on input picture
	- count TPs
	- drop pictures for OFF channel
	- parse PES and ES headers
	- check for first sequence header if it has not been read
	- scan PCR and set tbOffset
	- drop picture if either first sequence header or PCR is missing
	- check DTS if first DTS has not been read
	- time stamps mapping/recovery
	- relevant processing based on channel mode


