1/31/00
  - Found out that the DTS jump problem is due to the mis-assocaition of
    PES header with picture.  The current clean cut associate PES header
    with the picture whose first slice start code follows.  This is to support
    the stupid HITS source.  This however, is not standard compliance.
    The fix now implements the standard PES association with picture.

